videos.headline: Wydermyer hauls in 10-yard Aggies' TD
videos.description: Jalen Wydermyer lunges to the corner of the end zone to get a foot down for a Texas A&M touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wydermyer hauls in 10-yard Aggies' TD) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mond bulldozes in for short Aggies TD
videos.description: Kellen Mond pushes through traffic and gets into the end zone for a Texas A&M touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mond bulldozes in for short Aggies TD) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn lets easy interception turn into Texas A&M TD
videos.description: Kellen Mond's throw is deflected by an Auburn defender and lands in the hands of Jalen Wydermyer for a 20-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn lets easy interception turn into Texas A&M TD) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith runs in short Aggies' TD

videos.headline: Texas A&M hangs on to beat Auburn in back-and-forth battle
videos.description: After several lead changes, Texas A&M is able to hang on to beat Auburn, 31-20.
